character.name: Ancient Slime Boss - Legless
character.prompt: Gigantic ancient slime boss with a semi-transparent gelatinous body, glowing core pulsing with energy inside, dripping ooze, covered in bubbles and cracks. COMPLETELY LEGLESS - pure amorphous blob that spreads and oozes across the ground like liquid. No human limbs or appendages, just a massive gelatinous mass. Intimidating, heavy, and otherworldly presence. Designed for a dark fantasy top-down roguelike game.
